body_html: TFLiteObjectDetectionAPIModel was recently modified to use a different model, which as additional outputs (see this commit). If you want to continue using mobilenet_v1, pattern your code after the code before that commit. In particular, mobilenet_v1 only has outputLocations and outputClass. It does not have outputScores or numDetections.
